settings.body1Text: NSLOCTEXT("[FEA8EFE747B6BFEF48AD2AB3CBEF2B13]", "F60DE6754DE695C535019DB14F0E8D63", "Your {NodeName} Citizenship has been revoked because you did not pay your dues.\\n\\nItems in your {NodeName} node storage are no longer available")
